tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE market_data (
  symbol VARCHAR,
  price DECIMAL,
  volume INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE MarketData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(255),
  price DECIMAL,
  volume INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TradingDecisions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(255),
  decision VARCHAR(255),
  executed BOOLEAN,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ClientData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  client_id INT,
  symbol VARCHAR(255),
  investment DECIMAL,
  status VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE trading_history (
    trade_id VARCHAR(20),
    account_id VARCHAR(20),
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    trade_volume INT,
    trade_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE analysis_results (
    analysis_id VARCHAR(20),
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    trend VARCHAR(10),
    sentiment VARCHAR(20),
    analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trades(
  trade_id INT,
  client_id INT,
  symbol STRING,
  price DECIMAL,
  volume INT,
  trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history(
  trade_id INT,
  symbol STRING,
  trade_type STRING,
  trade_volume INT,
  trade_result STRING,
  trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
